uid":32723,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"b8175315fea9c2c0df3c7b4d410f43474d5b11cb","tid":2433353,"uid":330375,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"bcb549484d1dd773cd956d0df9cb33c140de703d","tid":2433353,"uid":89892,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-03-05T16:56:01.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-03-06T02:33:55.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/chicken.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-03-06T02:34:35.000Z","msg":"做呢行要忍<br />\n一係就　要爛口，　日日屌人老母"},{"pid":"be443f5b76e662b1c6e5af0730f019ac5a62fae3","tid":2433353,"uid":361846,"like":12,"dislike":1,"score":11,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-03-06T02:45:51.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/oh.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"2429081a797bc6765a34b0bf05b533a6ad32518e","tid":2433353,"uid":330375,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"6b776bd762e551bd7a4d47dadeee0959501b967e","tid":2433353,"uid":346446,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-03-05T17:37:08.000Z","msg":"樓主有冇考慮儲錢去海外讀物理治療"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-03-06T02:46:29.000Z","msg":"有架, 諗緊好唔好依加儲多d 錢先, 兩三年後再去外國讀個master."},{"pid":"e91d5bfc059125817dfe746a4e05f9c9992a0feb","tid":2433353,"uid":346446,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"2429081a797bc6765a34b0bf05b533a6ad32518e","tid":2433353,"uid":330375,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"6b776bd762e551bd7a4d47dadeee0959501b967e","tid":2433353,"uid":346446,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-03-05T17:37:08.000Z","msg":"樓主有冇考慮儲錢去海外讀物理治療"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-03-06T02:46:29.000Z","msg":"有架, 諗緊好唔好依加儲多d 錢先, 兩三年後再去外國讀個master."},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-03-06T03:48:12.000Z","msg":"加油，巴打<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"32a90225f34f55fc585afa792f139609f0c3e06d","tid":2433353,"uid":383137,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"quote":{"pid":"a868c164fd2163584e86ac4f6a9a77d4374f9fb6","tid":2433353,"uid":330375,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":3,"replyTime":"2021-03-05T01:16:28.000Z","msg":"開post 既目的係想比大家分享下自己工作前資料搜集不足而覺得中伏既經驗, 比諗住入行既睇下了解下實際情況都好<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n我自己本身做護士, 唔係首選工作, 入行係因為poly physio 門檻高到傻讀唔到<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 當年又未有咁多東華明愛戈d 課程, 於是就蹤左個頭埋去<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/banghead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 諗住入行再搵職位去做多d sports medicine 既野.<br />\n讀之前既認知就係呢行要執屎執尿, 成日面對死亡, 又要番通宵, 聽落都唔開胃. 不過勝在fresh grad 人工高, 諗住可以彌補番. 讀左之後反而覺得屎尿死亡調整下心理都可以豁然面對, 但係追更文化真係反人類發明黎. 普通追更係晏二晚九第日朝七晏二, 通宵就晚九朝七平均一個禮拜一次, 而且一定係同一日番完早更夜晚就番通宵, 者係再前一晚一定係痴住個晏晝更, 番到個人得番個殼<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/18.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 比你抖番兩日都回唔到狀態, 更加唔好話做運動<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 身邊仲要好似冇人覺得呢個做法有問題咁, 變左做傳統一代傳一代永無止境咁. 聽過有個原因係話咩想護士長d 時間對番同一班病人, 心諗屌你佢唔出院你唔好放工呀笨<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 唔好彩既你仲會遇到一班好似以前讀修女學校d 朋友口中好嚴好多要求既修女咁管住你既上司<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n同埋係個體制入面用護士個角色根本做唔到我想做既野, 理想同諗法同呢行既人都有出入, 所以早排就遞左信. 短短係呢行既一段時間都有遇過好人, 我都好衷心咁感激佢地既教導, 但係整體黎講我都係唔想留低. 黎緊做住agency 既護士先, 收入少左d 不過可以有個機會整理一下自己人生. <br />\n<br />\n我既故事到呢到, 有冇其他行業既師兄師姐可以分享下<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/biggrin.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />?"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-03-06T04:04:00.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/shocking.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"40032600422901a7b3b25df95c404862b577add5","tid":2433353,"uid":330375,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"be443f5b76e662b1c6e5af0730f019ac5a62fae3","tid":2433353,"uid":361846,"like":12,"dislike":1,"score":11,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-03-06T02:45:51.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/oh.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-03-06T04:20:48.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/biggrin.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b5ac36